  "detailed_description": "Harold's Walk is back and now he's walking around in your PC!<br><br>Explore 3D worlds and discover all the secret objects in Harold's Walk. Master the use of your special abilities to reach new areas.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1009360/extras/faa9acbccecc05b36a9bdbe40d4c020e.poster.avif?t=1721066026\" width=284 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1009360/extras/faa9acbccecc05b36a9bdbe40d4c020e.webm?t=1721066026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1009360/extras/faa9acbccecc05b36a9bdbe40d4c020e.mp4?t=1721066026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Veteran Harold's Walk players will recognize all the classic stages from the original handheld version of the game on Nintendo 3ds, plus new challenges, improved controls, and better graphics.<br><br>With a large batch of original never-before-seen content Harold's Walk on PC is worth a second lap around the track.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1009360/extras/67debd999230803f158baf0f0cc532dc.poster.avif?t=1721066026\" width=284 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1009360/extras/67debd999230803f158baf0f0cc532dc.webm?t=1721066026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1009360/extras/67debd999230803f158baf0f0cc532dc.mp4?t=1721066026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This new iteration of the Harold's Walk universe has :<br>-100 crowns to collect<br>-over 40 secret portals<br>-Over double the music of the original game<br>-Higher quality music, sound effects, and visuals<br><br>Plus more.",
